original_title: 田中れいな バースデーイベント おつかれいな 会5 ～27さいかぁっっ。～
overview: The DVD is separated into two volumes: the first features Tanaka's birthday event held at Shinjuku ReNY, and the second features her "Iwai 27sai! TRKIO (Tanaka Reina Kakkoii Otona ni Narou) Tour" with Joujou Gundan. Disc 1 (60mins), Disc 2 (67mins).
title: Tanaka Reina Birthday Event OtsukaReina Kai 5 ~27sai kaa.~
